graphicslib3D.Shape3D

  • Packages that use Shape3D 
    Package Description
    graphicslib3D.shape  

    • Uses of Shape3D in graphicslib3D.shape

      Subclasses of Shape3D in graphicslib3D.shape 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Sphere
      This class defines a sphere constructed by defining ring made up of vertices in the XZ plane and then making additional rings above and below it, progressively smaller towards the poles.
      class  Torus
      This class defines a torus constructed by first defining a ring made up of vertices in the XY plane and then sweeping copies of the ring about the Y axis.
